snippet.title: Longplay of MTV Sports: Pure Ride
snippet.description:
Longplay of MTV Sports: Pure Ride, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Color. This game's version was released on Sep. 28th, 2000. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:45 - MTV Qualification Canada
02:42 - Bitterroot Slopstyle
04:42 - San Juan Slopstyle
06:51 - East Karoo Slopstyle
09:06 - West Karoo Slopstyle

12:12 - Pure Ride Qualification Norway
13:39 - Bitterroot Slopstyle
15:36 - San Juan Slopstyle
17:48 - East Karoo Slopstyle
20:03 - West Karoo Slopstyle
22:12 - Norrland Halfpipe
24:52 - Jura Slopstyle
26:57 - Hautes Alpes Slopstyle

29:36 - Shrine San Slopstyle
32:14 - Yariga Take Slopstyle
34:44 - Norrland Halfpipe
38:21 - Big Horn Slopstyle

41:13 - End
41:40 - Credits

By: Terua
